high_descs: Go to the sink just ahead of you to your right.
Pick up the knife that is on the floor, in front of the sink.
Turn to your right and walk towards the wall, out of the kitchen, then turn to your right and go to the dining table in the left corner, ahead of you.
Place the knife on the white plate on the table, that is in front of the loaf of bread.
Pick up the plate with the knife on it from the table.
Turn to your right and go back into the main kitchen area, and make another right immediately after entering the kitchen to get to the sink across from you.
Place the plate with the knife still on it, in the right side of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate containing a knife in the sink.

high_descs: Go forward to the front of the sink on the left.
Pick up the yellow knife on the floor in front of the sink.
Turn around and go to the white round table in the right corner.
Place the knife on the white plate on the left of the bread.
Pick up the plate with the knife on it.
Turn around and go to the front of the sink on the right.
Place the plate with the knife on it inside the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the plate with the knife on it in the sink.

high_descs: turn to face sink
pick up sharp knife from inside sink
walk to face round table
put knife on plate on table
pick up plate from table
walk to face sink
put plate in sink basin
anns.task_desc: put plate and knife into sink
